隔离超时：优先级（全局+服务级别）
onsame网络异常、onnext隔离异常

protoc --go_out=. XXX.protoc
protobuf生成契约模板：

syntax = "proto3";
option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "io.grpc.examples.rpchandle";
option java_outer_classname = "rpchandleProto";

package rpchandle;

message RpcRequest {
string name = 1;
string age = 2;
string job = 3;
}

message RpcReply {
string ReplyMessage = 1;
}

pre-conditions:
   ide,go envionment,set GOPATH,CHASSIS_HOME
step 1:edit schema
    @highway(rpc) needs some tools include protoc,golang
        edit xxx.proto and make protoc file in cmd(protoc --go_out=filepath your xxx.proto)
    @rest
        edit operationId function and add a route for your function